Rabbit
------

A simple Click-Move-End game.

Use With: Mouse, Touch Screen, or Switch 

Mouse/Touch Screen:
Click the mouse/touch anywhere on the screen and a rabbit will appear.  The rabbit will hop towards the centre of the screen, and once there disappear again.

Switch:
Hitting the Switch will cause the rabbit to appear at a random location on the screen.  The rabbit will hop towards the centre of the screen, and once there disappear again.

Requirements
------------

The following files are needed from the game libraries:

ClickMoveEnd.lua
AnAL.lua

Credits
-------

Rabbit animation from: http://www.animationlibrary.com/animation/23994/Bunny_hops/
Music from: http://www.flashkit.com/loops/Easy_Listening/Instrumental/_In_T-Edgen-6900/index.php 
